TopicTitle: Is there a way to manually delete contracts in outside of the game?

Articles.Content: I'm playing the Alien Space Program mod and I can't complete the "Launch our first vessel" contract on Tylo or Minmus. Is there a way to manually complete the contract so I can actually do things in career mode? I think it's got something to do with airless worlds, because Duna still works.
In the alt-12 menu you can complete or delete contracts.
